frames.caption: In a dramatic scene under a rainy backdrop, a figure with a deer head and antlers walks confidently forward, flanked by two imposing characters. The central figure wears a red scarf and gold chains, exuding an air of authority and mystery.
frames.description: The scene is set in a dark, rainy environment, creating a tense and mysterious atmosphere. The central figure, a human with a deer head, leads the group with confidence, while two other characters follow closely, adding to the intensity of the moment.

frames.caption: A surreal scene features a humanoid figure with a deer head, adorned with a red scarf and gold chain, walking confidently. Flanked by two other figures, one resembling a muscular green character and another with a masked face, they stride across a wet, reflective surface. The atmosphere is mysterious and slightly ominous, enhanced by the dim lighting and rain.
frames.description: The scene is set in a dark, rainy environment with a reflective ground, creating a dramatic and surreal atmosphere. The central figure, a humanoid with a deer head, is the focal point, exuding confidence and mystery.
